## Component Hierarchy

```
app/
  page.tsx                  ← Home Dashboard
  stock/[ticker]/page.tsx   ← Stock Detail Page
  layout.tsx                ← Root layout (nav, theme)

components/
  signals/
    SignalCard.tsx           ← Compact dashboard card
    SignalExpanded.tsx       ← Full expanded view
    SignalRankList.tsx       ← Ranked list of signals
  news/
    NewsFeed.tsx
    NewsItem.tsx
  charts/
    PriceChart.tsx
    SentimentChart.tsx
    NewsVolumeChart.tsx
  heatmap/
    SectorHeatmap.tsx
  alerts/
    AlertBanner.tsx
  ui/                        ← Shared primitives (buttons, badges, cards)
```

---

## Data Fetching
- Fetch signals, news, and explanations from the FastAPI backend
- Use Next.js Server Components for initial data load
- Use client components + polling (or SWR) for near-real-time updates
- Do NOT expose backend API keys to the client
